name: Feeding Time (Hohenstaufer)
description:
It is the year of our space lord 792. Your new job is zookeeper in Space Zoo #78. Don't let the space zoo monsters starve or they will feast upon your succulent human flesh.

Feeding Time was made in GB Studio. You can play it online in your browser or on your smartphone. You can download the .pocket file to play it with an Analogue Pocket and you can download the .gb file to play it with a Game Boy emulator.

Feeding Time was made with the amazing GB Studio software. I created pixel art using Piskel. Music was made by TipTopTomCat and Krümel and was found on 8-bit Gameboy Songs GB Studio-page and in the GB Studio Community Assets.

Feeding Time was made in a week for the Gameboy Showdown. As such there are only 3 levels as of yet. I may add more later!

Controls

Game Boy Keyboard Move D-pad Arrow keys Interact A Z

Feedback

Feel free to leave a comment if you have any feedback concerning the game or if you encounter any bug.
